description=Turns runner zombies into living sirens with more than 60 unique human screams. Each sprinter gets its own voice that blends with the vanilla audio, and all behavior is configurable in the Sandbox (frequency, volume, time of day, activation chance). Designed for runs with 1–2% runners, where every scream matters, but with smart cooldown and cluster control to avoid sound spam even on crowded maps!!
